This strategy provides a roadmap through immediate turbulence to long-term stability. It prioritizes urgent economic stabilization while simultaneously laying the groundwork for deep structural changes in climate adaptation, inequality reduction, and democratic strengthening. Success hinges on decisive leadership, transparent communication, and the political courage to make difficult choices. By demonstrating tangible progress on these interconnected fronts, we can build confidence, rally national support, and secure a mandate for a resilient and equitable future.

